{"tid":142942,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"地產公司董事BMW遭低調縱火 燒埋老婆新座駕","createTime":"2017-03-04T08:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T18:23:15.000Z","uid":65346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"faa28117efafb4df4445ce37bf57961ac8fee7ef","tid":142942,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:18:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170304/56382880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170304%2F56382880&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=521013f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170304%2F56382880&h=4c7eb8a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170304/56382880</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n凌晨1時許，沙田馬鞍山錦英苑停車場C樓層，一輛寶馬X1起火焚燒，波及旁邊一輛奧迪A3，火勢猛烈及冒出濃煙，由途人發現報警。消防員接報到場，開1條喉及出動1隊煙帽隊灌救，將火救熄。寶馬嚴重焚毀，奧迪半邊車身亦告燒毀，另外兩輛豐田Corolla的油漆及燈殼燒溶。<br />\n消防調查認為火警起因有可疑，交由警方跟進。現場閉路電視拍攝到有兩名可疑男子，警方正展開追緝。兩人25至35歲，中等身材，案發時1人身穿淺色上衣、藍色牛仔褲；另1人身穿深色上衣、藍色牛仔褲及戴冷帽。<br />\n原來寶馬的車主，是世紀21奇豐物業董事莊振耀，而奧迪則是其妻的座駕。莊接受《蘋果》電話訪問否認結怨：「真係唔知道，我都搲晒頭，等差人查。」而妻子的奧迪落地未夠一年，雙雙燒毀十分無奈。"},{"pid":"fecb4217b16e57bd5b7d652cff5e2a9dfcbba52c","tid":142942,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:36:30.000Z","msg":"奧神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44cf68d8d31d7b92c8bb6e1adf3ceac5d2bb51df","tid":142942,"uid":42661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"董事 錦英苑 X1 A3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86db18ab01a4da287806c56ad072419202c408b","tid":142942,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:04:19.000Z","msg":"咩低調縱火？"},{"pid":"ef04a40c69e029459f72bf71b0c88e0b8fbdb730","tid":142942,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩低調縱火？</blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22eadf790fc032da63f0b96a5f3775d931d12f6","tid":142942,"uid":4896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩低調縱火？</blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e36f1d949427ebb4f2f4db6c244550b13ed174","tid":142942,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩低調縱火？</blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+2"},{"pid":"b359784430b3ca52406cc9dbb6daeb2406bebc38","tid":142942,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩低調縱火？</blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入黎就係想問呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b59c7ce2ea6f735923904b0b390bc6715534862","tid":142942,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"有咩咁好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"h